    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "return $input.all().map(item => {\n\nconst memo = item.json;\n\nconst systemPrompt = `\nYou are the virtual receptionist for ${memo.company_name}.\n\nBUSINESS HOURS\n${memo.business_hours.days.join(\", \")}\n${memo.business_hours.start} - ${memo.business_hours.end}\n\nSERVICES OFFERED\n${memo.services_supported.join(\", \")}\n\nOFFICE HOURS FLOW\n1. Greet caller\n2. Ask purpose of call\n3. Collect caller name and phone number\n4. Determine service request\n5. Schedule appointment or route call\n6. Confirm next steps\n7. Ask if anything else is needed\n8. End call politely\n\nAFTER HOURS FLOW\n1. Greet caller\n2. Determine if emergency\n3. If emergency:\n   - Collect name\n   - Collect phone number\n   - Collect address\n   - Attempt transfer to technician\n4. If transfer fails:\n   - Apologize\n   - Inform technician will call back shortly\n\nEMERGENCY DEFINITION\n${memo.emergency_definition.join(\", \")}\n`;\n\nconst agentSpec = {\n  agent_name: `${memo.company_name} Assistant`,\n  voice_style: \"professional\",\n  version: \"v1\",\n\n  variables: {\n    company_name: memo.company_name,\n    business_hours: memo.business_hours,\n    services_supported: memo.services_supported,\n    emergency_definition: memo.emergency_definition\n  },\n\n  system_prompt: systemPrompt,\n\n  transfer_protocol: {\n    strategy: \"immediate_transfer\",\n    retries: 2,\n    timeout: \"20 seconds\"\n  },\n\n  fallback_protocol: {\n    action: \"collect_caller_info\",\n    message: \"Our technician will call you shortly.\"\n  }\n};\n\nreturn {\njson:{\naccount_id: memo.account_id,\nagent_spec: agentSpec\n}\n};\n\n});"
      },
